Description: Comedy Takes Center Stage with Louis RAMEY & Kristin KEY.Welcome to the only place in Las Vegas to catch Brad Garrett performing live along with some of the hottest names in stand-up - from established stars to the funniest up-and-comers. To add to the fun factor, every show takes place in a specially designed theater custom-built for comedy.
Location: 3770 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
